  "reference_number": "RUS3040",
  "remarks": "\nZamid Alievich CHALAYEV is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the grounds that he is or has been involved in\n destabilising Ukraine or undermining or threatening the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine as a person who is (1) a member of the armed forces or law-enforcement organs of the Russian Federation of the rank of colonel, or equivalent, or higher and (2) responsible for, engages in, provides support for, or promotes policies or actions which destabilise Ukraine or undermines or threatens the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine. \n",
